time_series_with_forecast.query: q = load "${App.Datasets.opportunity_revinsights.FullyQualifiedName}"; q = filter q by 'ForecastCategory' == "Closed"; k = group q by all; k = foreach k generate "2000" as 'Date_Year', "01" as 'Date_Month', "01" as 'Date_Day'; k = group k by ('Date_Year', 'Date_Month', 'Date_Day'); k = foreach k generate 'Date_Year', 'Date_Month', 'Date_Day', count() as 'sum'; k = fill k by (dateCols=('Date_Year','Date_Month','Date_Day', "Y-M-D")); k = timeseries k generate 'sum' as 'cnt' with (length=10000,  dateCols=('Date_Year','Date_Month','Date_Day', "Y-M-D")); k = filter k by {{row(CloseDate_1.selection, [0], ["min", "max"]).asDateRange("date('Date_Year','Date_Month', 'Date_Day')")}}; k = filter k by date('Date_Year','Date_Month', 'Date_Day') in [.."current day"]; k = group k by all; k1 = foreach k generate first('Date_Year') as 'CloseDate_Year', first('Date_Month') as 'CloseDate_Month', first('Date_Day') as 'CloseDate_Day', 0 as 'A'; k2 = foreach k generate last('Date_Year') as 'CloseDate_Year', last('Date_Month') as 'CloseDate_Month', last('Date_Day') as 'CloseDate_Day'; k3 = union k1,k2; a = group q by ('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day'); a = foreach a generate 'CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day', sum(q.'Amount') as 'A'; c = union a,k3; c = foreach c generate 'CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day', 'A'; c = fill c by (dateCols=('CloseDate_Year','CloseDate_Month','CloseDate_Day', "Y-M-D")); c = filter c by date('CloseDate_Year','CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day') in [.."current day"]; result = group c by ('CloseDate_Year', 'CloseDate_Month', 'CloseDate_Day'); result = foreach result generate c.'CloseDate_Year' + "~~~" + c.'CloseDate_Month' + "~~~" + c.'CloseDate_Day' as 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day', first('A') as 'A'; result = group result by 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day'; result = foreach result generate 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day', first(A) as 'A', sum(sum(A)) over ([..0] partition by all order by ('CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day')) as 'Cumulative_Amount'; result = order result by ('CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day' asc); start_forecast = group result by all; start_forecast = foreach start_forecast generate last('CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day') as 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day', last('Cumulative_Amount') as 'Cumulative_Amount'; start_forecast = foreach start_forecast generate case when 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day' < "{{cell(intermediate_date_step.result, 0, "start_day").asString()}}" then "{{cell(intermediate_date_step.result, 0, "start_day").asString()}}" else 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day' end as 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day', 'Cumulative_Amount'; a1 = load "${App.Datasets.opportunity_revinsights.FullyQualifiedName}"; a1 = group a1 by all; end_forecast = foreach a1 generate "{{cell(intermediate_date_step.result, 0, "end_day").asString()}}" as 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day', {{coalesce(cell(soql_user_commit_forecast.result, 0, "ForecastAmount"),0).asString()}} as 'Cumulative_Amount'; forecast_line = union start_forecast, end_forecast; final = group result by 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day' full, forecast_line by 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day'; final = foreach final generate coalesce(result['CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day'], forecast_line['CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day']) as 'CloseDate_Year~~~CloseDate_Month~~~CloseDate_Day', first(result['Cumulative_Amount']) as 'Closed Won Sales', first(forecast_line['Cumulative_Amount']) as 'Commit Forecast';
